casebody.data:
No. 10-1450. Sonic-Calabasas A, Inc., Petitioner v. Frank Moreno. 565 U.S. 973, 132 S. Ct. 496,

181 L. Ed. 2d 343,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7728. October 31, 2011.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of California. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of California for further consideration in light of AT&T Mobility LLC v. Concepcion, 563 U.S. 333, 131 S. Ct. 1740, 179 L. Ed. 2d 742 (2011).

Same case below, 51 Cal. 4th 659, 121 Cal. Rptr. 3d 58, 247 P.3d 130.
